text: Sandra Ida Christina Bergqvist (born 14 April 1980 at Nagu) is a Finnish politician, member of the Parliament since 2019 as well as the chairperson of the Swedish Assembly of Finland. == References == Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:People from Pargas Category:Swedish-speaking Finns Category:Swedish People's Party of Finland politicians Category:Members of the Parliament of Finland (2019–23) Category:21st-century Finnish women politicians Category:Åbo Akademi University alumni
title: Sandra Bergqvist
